023/7/14/23795311/hollywood-strike-wga-sag-aftra-streaming&quot;>;也开始罢工&lt;/a>;）。这次罢工并非没有造成人员伤亡。据报道，本周早些时候，亚马逊将责任归咎于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/18/23837756/cancelling-a-show-because-of-the-hollywood-strikes-is-certainly -a-move&quot;>;重新取消其&lt;em>;他们自己的联盟​​&lt;/em>;罢工电视连续剧的可疑选择，以及翻拍弗里茨·朗的无声电影经典&lt;em>;大都会&lt;/ em>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theguardian.com/film/2023/jun/20/apple-tv-remake-of-sci-fi-classic-metropolis-cancelled-due-to-us-writers -strike&quot;>;是...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/19/23838283/striking-writers-have-been-与工作室的持续对话超过一周&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/19/23838283/striking-writers-have-been-in-consistent-talks-with-studios-for-over-a-week" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/19/23838283/striking-writers-have-been-in-concient-talks-with-studios-for-over-a-week</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-08-19T10:44:30-04:00</published><updated> 2023-08-19T10:44:30-04:00</updated><title>今天是 PS5 及其多彩 DualSense 控制器优惠的最后一天</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;基于光盘的 PlayStation 5 的库存照片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/pavaaRlKaabDcwF3P2hb8eCeMYw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn .com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72559003/vpavic_4278_20201030_0345.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;多家零售商现在也在打折 PS5，这意味着您不一定需要从索尼购买它。&lt; /em>; |图片：索尼&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;FvVVMX&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21550146/sony-playstation-5-ps5-review&quot;>; 上的优惠&lt;strong>;PlayStation 5&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>; 千载难逢。这就是为什么我们在这里提醒您索尼出色的 PS5 促销活动 - 其中有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/6/23820082/so​​ny-playstation-5-disc-edition- Dualsense-wireless-controller-deal-sale&quot;>;自 8 月 6 日起开始运行&lt;/a>;，作为索尼大型夏季特卖的一部分 — 将于太平洋时间今晚 11:59 结束。在此之前，您可以在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0